excerpt.rendered:
DESCRIPTION
Share your American pride with your pup while taking doggie playtime to another level with this Top Paw Americana Plush Bone Dog Toy. This fun toy comes in the shape of a bone, features a classic red, white, and blue design, and keeps dogs entertained and engaged with the playful squeaking sounds it makes when played with. Only at PetSmart.

Features:

Dog Bone toy
Red, White, and Blue design
Internal squeaker promotes play

Includes: 1 Toy

Intended For: Dog

Activity: Noisemaking

Color: Red, White, Blue

Dimensions: 7.5 in

Advice for Use:
Observe your pet’s behavior with the toy for suitability. Some toys may be inappropriate for your pet. Remove and replace the toy if it becomes damaged. This product is intended for dog use only.

Caution:
Ingestion of this product can result in serious injury.

Buy this product on petsmart.com
